<messaging:emailTemplate subject="You have a new PAF approval request: {!relatedTo.Name} - {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_PAF_Customer__r.Name}" recipientType="User" relatedToType="ASI_HK_CRM_Pre_Approval_Form__c"><messaging:htmlEmailBody ><html>    <body>    <STYLE type="text/css">        BODY { font-size: 15px }        H2 { font-size: 15px }        P { font-size: 16px; margin: 14px 0}        TH {font-size: 12px; font-face: arial;background: #CCCCCC; border-width: 1;  text-align: center }         TD  {font-size: 12px; font-face: verdana }         TABLE {border: solid #CCCCCC; border-width: 1}        TR {border: solid #CCCCCC; border-width: 1}     </STYLE>        <p>You have a new pre-approval form approval request, the details are as follows:</p>     <p><b>Pre-Approval Form Number:</b> {!relatedTo.Name}<br/>        <b>Start Date:</b>        <apex:outputText value="{0, date, dd/MM/yyyy}"><apex:Param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_PAF_Start_Date__c}" /></apex:OutputText><br/>         <b>End Date: </b>        <apex:outputText value="{0, date, dd/MM/yyyy}"><apex:Param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_PAF_End_Date__c}" /></apex:OutputText><br/>         <b>No. of Months:</b> {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_PAF_No_of_Months__c}<br/>         <b>Volume Commitment:</b> {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_PAF_Volume_Commitment__c}<br/>         <b>Contract Requirement:</b> {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_PAF_Contract_Requirement__c}<br/>         <b>Version No.:</b> {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_PAF_Version_No__c}<br/>         <b>Raised Date:</b>        <apex:outputText value="{0, date, dd/MM/yyyy}"><apex:Param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_PAF_Raised_Date__c}" /></apex:OutputText> <br/>         <b>Nature of Promotion:</b> {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_PAF_Nature_of_Promotion__c}<br/>         <b>Total Sales Value:</b>          <apex:outputText value="{0, Number, Currency}" >        <apex:param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_SYS_Total_SKU_Value_1__c}" />        </apex:outputText>                 <br/>          <b>Total Investment Value:</b>           <apex:outputText value="{0, Number, Currency}" >        <apex:param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_Total_Investment_Value__c}" />        </apex:outputText>        <br/>         <b>Total Investment%:</b> {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_Total_Investment__c}<br/>         <b>Variable Fund Investment Exceeded for any Sub-brand?:</b> {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_All_Sub_Brand_VFI_Threshold__c}<br/>         <b>Contract Details:</b> {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_Contract_Details__c}<br/>         <b>Conditions of Payment:</b> {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_Conditions_of_Payment__c}<br/>         <b>Other Comments:</b> {!relatedTo.ASI_HK_CRM_Other_Comments__c}<br/>      </p>      <p>Details: <apex:outputlink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140,FIND('.com',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+4)+relatedTo.Id}">      {!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140,FIND('.com',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+4)+relatedTo.Id}            </apex:outputlink></p>      <p>Note: For salesforce.com to process your response the word <font style="color:red">APPROVE, APPROVED, YES, REJECT, REJECTED</font>, or NO must be in the very first line of the reply email. Also, any comment must be in the second line.      </p>         <c:ASI_CRM_HK_PAF_ApprovalEmailMech headerId="{!relatedTo.Id}" />             <p />        </body>    </html></messaging:htmlEmailBody> <messaging:plainTextEmailBody ></messaging:plainTextEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>